snippet.title: Meta is Back! Segment Anything 3 is Here (Open Weight)
snippet.description:
Meta release segment anything model 3 along with SAM 3D, a unified model for detection, segmentation, and tracking of objects in images and video using text, exemplar, and visual prompts.

https://ai.meta.com/blog/segment-anything-model-3/
https://www.aidemos.meta.com/segment-anything/gallery
https://github.com/facebookresearch/sam3
https://ai.meta.com/sam3d/
https://colab.research.google.com/github/roboflow-ai/notebooks/blob/main/notebooks/how-to-segment-images-with-segment-anything-3.ipynb
https://colab.research.google.com/github/roboflow-ai/notebooks/blob/main/notebooks/how-to-segment-videos-with-segment-anything-3.ipynb
